	<Title>
		Early HIV symptoms: What are they?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Early HIV signs and symptoms may include fever, fatigue and swollen lymph glands. Learn more.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		When do early HIV symptoms first appear?
	</Question>
